{"root":{"data":{"id":"dj1pg3vrf0w0","created":1780722510292,"text":"单片机CMS8S5880主控","expandState":"expand","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1phcgg3600","created":1780722607321,"text":"电源电路","font-size":18,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1qzv4iln40","created":1780726879624,"text":"开关机：\nPOWER按键(S1)短按，单片机引脚P13锁存控制，输出高电平开机；\n按键长按2秒，P13低电平关断电源关机。","font-size":16,"priority":null,"progress":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1r7wvwl8o0","created":1780727510370,"text":"电池电量监测：开机状态时，单片机引脚P04检测ADC分压值，从而检测电池电量","font-size":16,"progress":2},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dj1phcykczc0","created":1780722608417,"text":"测量电路","font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1sglgemy80","created":1780731011875,"text":"单片机引脚P22--74HC4060D的Q13引脚","progress":1,"font-size":16},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1synirgjc0","created":1780732426926,"text":"通过控制引脚P22输入激励信号，改变4060分频振荡频率；\nFE，低频率； NFE，高频率","progress":2},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1t0c4rdy80","created":1780732558863,"text":"单片机引脚P36接收反馈信号ADC值","progress":3},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1t11b6ktk0","created":1780732613671,"text":"MCU计算漆面厚度","progress":4},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dj1phdrt7n40","created":1780722610185,"text":"人机交互模块","font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1t270yz480","created":1780732704479,"text":"背光板","progress":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1t2rzivlk0","created":1780732750104,"text":"按键S3按下，MCU引脚P25低电平"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1t5bovb9c0","created":1780732949723,"text":"再次按下，P25高电平"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dj1t2let7mg0","created":1780732735791,"text":"蜂鸣器","progress":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1t5la8n8g0","created":1780732970607,"text":"MCU检测到按键按下、测量完成，MCU引脚P24高电平"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dj1t2oa51aw0","created":1780732742038,"text":"屏幕","progress":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1t9dyyav40","created":1780733268143,"text":"MCU引脚P16  P17  P23  --  屏幕驱动芯片"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}